articles.title: About me
articles.contents:
Hey there!
I am Prachi, a student at Monash University.
I am currently pursuing a Master’s degree in Business Analytics (2021 to 2023), and I have graduated in Engineering of Information Technology from India. I am very much excited to share my thoughts and ideas with you all with the help of blogs. I hope you find my blogs interesting and informative.
You can check out my GitHub page for more exciting analysis.

articles.title: Blogs
articles.contents:
Introduction
Hi friends, I am Prachi.
Welcome to my blog, InfoNest. You can find a variety of informative and fun articles listed below. I am very much excited to share my thoughts and ideas with you all. I hope you guys find my blogs interesting and engaging.
Currently, I have one article (Peru’s Covid-19 situation), but stay tuned for more information on other topics too.!!
